00:19:37.250 --> 00:19:40.620
chakras are bulging out.

00:19:40.620 --> 00:19:44.810
Other person can tell you these are the portions
which are bulging out.

00:19:44.810 --> 00:19:50.020
So you go on saying the mantras of that chakra
paying attention and the other person can

00:19:50.020 --> 00:19:52.730
tell you whether it is all right or not.

00:19:52.730 --> 00:19:57.050
For every chakra there is a mantra, which
you know.

00:19:57.050 --> 00:20:05.370
Apart from mantra, you must know what things
should be used which element should be used

00:20:05.370 --> 00:20:08.030
for which chakra.

00:20:08.030 --> 00:20:15.200
For example, for using say, Mooladhara chakra,
best way to clear out Mooladhara chakra is

00:20:15.200 --> 00:20:17.231
sit on the ground.

00:20:17.231 --> 00:20:18.231
It’s the best way.

00:20:18.231 --> 00:20:24.330
I’ve told you how to do the exercise to
be able to sit on the ground straight, it’s

00:20:24.330 --> 00:20:31.680
very good idea of asking the mother earth
to clear out your Mooladhara.

00:20:31.680 --> 00:20:41.550
For say example, if you have to clear out
say your Nabhi, for Nabhi is made out of the

00:20:41.550 --> 00:20:50.820
water element and that’s why you have to
ask the water element to help you.

00:20:50.820 --> 00:20:53.500
And for Nabhi water element is the best.

00:20:53.500 --> 00:20:59.260
If you can use the water element to clear
your Nabhi, it will be a very good idea.

00:20:59.260 --> 00:21:05.020
Like that, every chakra is made from some
element as it is.

00:21:05.020 --> 00:21:14.640
Swadisthana is made of earth and water; so
the sea is the best for Swadhistana.

00:21:14.640 --> 00:21:19.680
If you could go to the sea and work out on
Swadhisthana, will be the best for you.

00:21:19.680 --> 00:21:28.420
In the ocean or you can use salt and water
for Swadhisthana; will be very good.

