00:22:02.390 --> 00:22:07.530
Air or you call it air as an element you call
the word air?

00:22:07.530 --> 00:22:09.280
Or firmament?

00:22:09.280 --> 00:22:12.470
Firmament is ether, in English isn’t it?

00:22:12.470 --> 00:22:18.520
So air, you can say air, air element is for
the heart chakra.

00:22:18.520 --> 00:22:23.860
So for that, I have told you how to do, I
mean, breathing.

