Breathing is the best way of hold your breath
before the photograph.

00:22:29.250 --> 00:22:36.870
Or you can take the breath in, deep breathing
and releasing it for a longer period.

00:22:36.870 --> 00:22:40.650
Cleaning it, all these exercises are there.

00:22:40.650 --> 00:22:47.640
Then you see the mantra is of raksha, is the
protection, to ask for the protection is all

00:22:47.640 --> 00:22:48.950
with the air.

00:22:48.950 --> 00:22:51.550
All right?

00:22:51.550 --> 00:23:32.190
Then we come to this one is here is
the akash, must be firmament.

00:23:32.190 --> 00:23:35.900
What is a firmament in English?

00:23:35.900 --> 00:23:38.380
Ether?

00:23:38.380 --> 00:23:39.380
Firmament is ether?

00:23:39.380 --> 00:23:45.530
All right, so this is the firmament, you see,
I read one translation but I was not sure.

00:23:45.530 --> 00:23:47.770
This is the akash, is the sky.

00:23:47.770 --> 00:23:51.960
This is the sky, here, all right?

00:23:51.960 --> 00:24:02.540
This is made out of the sky firmament and
this is made out of the light.

00:24:02.540 --> 00:24:07.780
Firmament is sky, is it?

00:24:07.780 --> 00:24:15.750
So this is sky; that’s why it is Virata
this thing.

00:24:15.750 --> 00:24:19.590
And this is your light.

00:24:19.590 --> 00:24:23.720
So for Agnya chakra you have to use the light,
for this you have to use the sky.

00:24:23.720 --> 00:24:28.330
If your hands put up like this if you say
“Allah hu Akbar” put both the hands towards

00:24:28.330 --> 00:24:29.590
the sky.

00:24:29.590 --> 00:24:30.590
See like that.

00:24:30.590 --> 00:24:35.190
There are so many ways of using the sky, watching
the sky, looking at the sky.

00:24:35.190 --> 00:24:41.800
And for this the sun and the light is to be
used.

00:24:41.800 --> 00:24:47.450
Now supposing you are suffering from say left
side problem, is sort of you’re possessed

00:24:47.450 --> 00:24:52.860
or something, then you can use the sun you
see because the sun will give you balance.

00:24:52.860 --> 00:24:57.420
But if you have the right side problems, like
ego and all that you should use the moon,

00:24:57.420 --> 00:24:59.550
put the left hand towards the moon.

00:24:59.550 --> 00:25:04.330
But always people do the other way round say
these dramatic melodramatic people you see,

00:25:04.330 --> 00:25:09.750
all of them will go to the lunar side in them,
they like the moonlight.

00:25:09.750 --> 00:25:15.120
And those who are egoistical will go in the
sun and burn themselves off.

00:25:15.120 --> 00:25:16.860
So other way round it should be.

00:25:16.860 --> 00:25:20.800
Like that if you use, you can work it out.

00:25:20.800 --> 00:25:23.160
All right?

00:25:23.160 --> 00:25:24.710
You yourself can manage it.

00:25:24.710 --> 00:25:32.390
So these are different centers, which must
be cleansed and meditated onto and or to be

00:25:32.390 --> 00:25:34.060
dissolved into their own.

00:25:34.060 --> 00:25:41.620
I mean if you dissolve them into their own
element, then you get more strength you see

00:25:41.620 --> 00:25:44.170
into that particular body.

00:25:44.170 --> 00:25:46.570
It’s like that.

00:25:46.570 --> 00:25:57.060
Sahaja Yogi: Can you tell us a bit about sunset;
are we not to look at the sunset?

