00:30:00.000 --> 00:30:05.240
cancer of kidneys, cancer of lungs; all of
them had this.

00:30:05.240 --> 00:30:10.910
That means somewhere a guru or somebody or
some black magic or spiritualist or something

00:30:10.910 --> 00:30:18.740
like that, he has intervened with the personality,
and then you get this cancer business.

00:30:18.740 --> 00:30:23.840
It’s a remarkable thing.

00:30:23.840 --> 00:30:31.830
Sahaja Yogini: Does the heat always indicate
a cancer problem?

00:30:31.830 --> 00:30:33.590
Shri Mataji: Cancer?

00:30:33.590 --> 00:30:35.929
No no no no.

00:30:35.929 --> 00:30:38.420
No no no no no no.

00:30:38.420 --> 00:30:42.660
Heat indicates liver, mainly liver.

00:30:42.660 --> 00:30:44.360
All right?

00:30:44.360 --> 00:30:49.740
And cancer is also; it’s when the cells
become ego-oriented, you see, a person who

00:30:49.740 --> 00:30:55.300
is ego oriented, they think too much, they
work very hard, means they get liver.

00:30:55.300 --> 00:30:56.300
You see?

