Because one center has to do the liver, the
pancreas, the spleen, the kidneys and uterus.

00:31:07.110 --> 00:31:08.110
Imagine.

00:31:08.110 --> 00:31:13.450
And the same has to make -look after the cells
for the brain, the same center, Swadisthana.

