00:32:51.170 --> 00:32:57.940
You see and he always sings songs of such
cry, I mean such a man I don’t know how

00:32:57.940 --> 00:33:00.790
he developed this kind of a melodramatic stuff.

00:33:00.790 --> 00:33:06.450
But I’ve known people who came to Me who
have been just crying reading this Lord Byron.

00:33:06.450 --> 00:33:13.030
He himself enjoyed life very well.

00:33:13.030 --> 00:33:20.510
So one has to take a very, very wise and sane
attitude towards life.

00:33:20.510 --> 00:33:30.970
That you are the eternal life, that you are
the eternal being and you have come on this

00:33:30.970 --> 00:33:36.450
earth to enjoy all the blessings that God
has created and not for weeping and crying

00:33:36.450 --> 00:33:37.450
and feeling guilty.

00:33:37.450 --> 00:33:38.470
That’s not your job.

00:33:38.470 --> 00:33:39.470
First thing is that.

00:33:39.470 --> 00:33:40.470
This is wisdom.

00:33:40.470 --> 00:33:47.080
And you are not going to make miserable about
small, small things of life also.

00:33:47.080 --> 00:33:52.280
Like the other day I saw a very interesting
story of a husband wife quarreling ending

00:33:52.280 --> 00:33:55.840
up into a divorce and poor husband had no
house, you see.

00:33:55.840 --> 00:33:57.620
So he went to his brother’s place.

00:33:57.620 --> 00:34:01.860
The brother’s wife very particular about
everything; she had three pets.

00:34:01.860 --> 00:34:08.330
So he could not put the box anywhere because
she would say.

00:34:08.330 --> 00:34:09.740
“No no no no no!

00:34:09.740 --> 00:34:11.149
There is another pet here!”

00:34:11.149 --> 00:34:13.130
Again, poor thing would lift it up.

00:34:13.130 --> 00:34:14.830
Then, “No no no no no!

00:34:14.830 --> 00:34:15.830
Not there!

00:34:15.830 --> 00:34:16.990
There is another pet; then another there like
that you see.

00:34:16.990 --> 00:34:24.530
All the time worried about small, small petty
things of life.

00:34:24.530 --> 00:34:27.050
Also that can create a problem of ego orientation.

00:34:27.050 --> 00:34:31.190
Live in a very carefree manner.

00:34:31.190 --> 00:34:37.409
It’s not so important but that doesn’t
mean laziness.

00:34:37.409 --> 00:34:40.340
I must tell you that doesn’t mean la – zi
–ness.

00:34:40.340 --> 00:34:44.419
Spell it with capital letters, all of you.

00:34:44.419 --> 00:34:58.290
By any chance it doesn’t mean that; it means
hard work – but enjoy it and not to be involved

00:34:58.290 --> 00:35:05.820
into things, which are of no importance at
all, useless things.

00:35:05.820 --> 00:35:11.400
Here it is joy spread for you.

00:35:11.400 --> 00:35:18.820
Why are you bothered about these things?

00:35:18.820 --> 00:35:25.869
They’re not meant for you.

00:35:25.869 --> 00:35:28.690
Isn’t it?

