petals, but you need not do all that.

00:36:11.140 --> 00:36:15.070
If you just say the innermost thing is Virat.

00:36:15.070 --> 00:36:17.930
There is no need to have the sounds or anything.

00:36:17.930 --> 00:36:25.920
Just you say “Virat” and it opens out.

00:36:25.920 --> 00:36:39.950
No use knowing, unnecessary, because we have
gone to the center most part, you see, called

00:36:39.950 --> 00:36:42.330
as the Brahma nadi.

00:36:42.330 --> 00:36:49.160
You see, if you have to go, say, from the
leaf to the root, then you have to know all

00:36:49.160 --> 00:36:50.160
the way.

00:36:50.160 --> 00:36:56.910
But if you are coming from the root, inside
the root, then what is the need?

00:36:56.910 --> 00:37:05.570
When they move that way, then only they knew
all these things.

00:37:05.570 --> 00:37:14.720
Say, in this house or in any building, you
have a lift just in the center, you see, and

00:37:14.720 --> 00:37:15.720
moving upward.

00:37:15.720 --> 00:37:17.040
You don’t have to know.

00:37:17.040 --> 00:37:18.710
You just move.

00:37:18.710 --> 00:37:24.680
But, if you have to come from outside every
time, every chakra, you will never be able

00:37:24.680 --> 00:37:26.740
to enter inside the lift.

00:37:26.740 --> 00:37:33.859
But you’ll be doing all; you will know everything
about that particular chakra from outside.

00:37:33.859 --> 00:37:39.430
But you’ll never get in; it is all the sympathetic
movement.

00:37:39.430 --> 00:37:45.640
So there is no need to know; like this I was
telling you, this is the center and this is

00:37:45.640 --> 00:37:47.440
the left and this is the right.

00:37:47.440 --> 00:37:50.750
You can come from the left and go back to
the left or you come from the left and go

00:37:50.750 --> 00:37:51.750
to the right.

00:37:51.750 --> 00:37:56.250
But, you cannot get inside and this inside
getting is the point.

00:37:56.250 --> 00:38:01.240
That’s the way you do it.

00:38:01.240 --> 00:38:02.240
All right?

00:38:02.240 --> 00:38:03.240
So there is no need to, this is all again
rambling.

